---
title: SaaS 平台請求流程（推理請求）
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用戶 (CLI/Web)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant QS as Quota Service
    participant IG as Inference Gateway
    participant Redis as Redis Cluster
    participant Kafka as Kafka
    participant NVIDIA as NVIDIA Endpoints
    participant UC as Usage Consumer
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    User->>GW: POST /api/v1/inference/chat\nAuthorization: Bearer JWT

    GW->>Auth: 驗證 JWT（公鑰驗證）
    Auth-->>GW: tenant_id, plan, permissions

    GW->>QS: 檢查配額\n(tenant_id, estimated_tokens)
    QS->>Redis: GET tenant:{id}:quota:tokens:used
    Redis-->>QS: 450000 (已使用)
    QS->>Redis: GET tenant:{id}:quota:tokens:limit
    Redis-->>QS: 1000000 (上限)

    alt 配額充足
        QS-->>GW: ✅ 允許（剩餘 550000）

        GW->>IG: 轉發推理請求\n(注入 tenant 上下文)

        IG->>Redis: 速率限制檢查\n(Sliding Window)
        Redis-->>IG: ✅ 允許 (59 RPM 剩餘)

        IG->>NVIDIA: POST /v1/chat/completions\n(使用平台 API Key)
        NVIDIA-->>IG: 推理回應\n{input: 150, output: 450 tokens}

        IG->>Kafka: 發布 usage.inference.completed\n{tenant_id, input:150, output:450}

        IG-->>GW: 回應 + Token 使用量
        GW-->>User: 200 OK + 推理結果

        Note over Kafka,PG: 非同步處理（不影響主流程）
        Kafka->>UC: 消費 usage 事件
        UC->>Redis: INCRBY tenant:{id}:tokens:used 600
        UC->>PG: INSERT inference_usage\n(tenant_id, sandbox_id, tokens, latency)

    else 配額不足
        QS-->>GW: ❌ 配額耗盡

        GW-->>User: 402 Payment Required\n{"error": "TOKEN_QUOTA_EXCEEDED",\n"upgrade_url": "..."}
    end
